    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individuae trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/130">Heinricus</persName> divina favente clementia
                        Romanorum <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Si sanctorum dei
                        ecclesiis ex nostris rebus aliquid offerimus, presentis et aeterne vitae
                        bravium adipisci non titubamus. Quapropter omnium sancte dei ecclesie
                        fidelium nostrorumque presentium ac futurorum industria noverit, qualiter
                        pro dei amore animeque nostre remedio per huius nostri precepti paginam
                        concedimus donamus atque largimur et omnimodis confirmamus ad stipendium et
                        usum atque sumptum fratrum <rs key="#Monks">monachorum</rs> in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">cenobio</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1450"
                            key="#Cartula #Venditio #Curtes #Mansi #Landed_possessions #Castle #Decima #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Churches #Monasteries #Royal_slave"
                            >sancte Florae</orgName> deo famulantium quandam <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1451">in honore sancte Mariae</orgName>
                        constructam in <placeName ref="#places/2721">monte Ionio</placeName> sitam
                        cum omnibus <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> rebus <rs key="#Mansi"
                            >mansis</rs> et <rs key="#Royal_slave">familiis</rs> ad eam in integrum
                        pertinentibus nec non et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">campum</rs> iuxta
                        eandem ecclesiam <rs key="#Fiscal_property">regiae potestati</rs> actenus
                        pertinentem atque <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2351">Barbaritanos</geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2354">Martinenses</geogName> similiter iuris regni nostri
                        pertinentes cum omnibus rebus et terris coniacentibus in <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/1403">Aretino</geogName> quae
                        dicuntur Martinenses et Barbaritane in locis et fundis qu[i] dicuntur
                            <placeName ref="#places/2754">Galognanum</placeName> et <rs
                            key="#Castle">castrum</rs> in <placeName ref="#places/2753"
                            >Quarata</placeName> et <placeName ref="#places/2721">monte
                            Ionio</placeName> in <placeName ref="#places/2755">Lvcignano</placeName>
                        et <placeName>Ficarita</placeName> et item <placeName ref="#places/2756"
                            >Lucignano</placeName>, <placeName ref="#places/2758"
                            >Quilliano</placeName> et <placeName ref="#places/2759"
                            >Carna</placeName> atque <placeName ref="#places/2760"
                            >Orneta</placeName>, <placeName ref="#places/2761">Uesigie</placeName>
                        et <rs key="#Castle">castellum</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/2762">Foconianum</placeName> in
                            <placeName>Marcena</placeName> et <placeName ref="#places/2763"
                            >Sesto</placeName> atque <placeName>Lina</placeName> et in
                            <placeName>Carpinito</placeName> et <placeName>Campo
                            Barbarensi</placeName> cum omnibus earum pertinentiis a <placeName
                            ref="#places/2764">Sibiano</placeName> usque <rs key="#Rivers">Classem
                            flumen</rs> ab <rs key="#Rivers">Arno</rs> usque <placeName
                            ref="#places/2765">Matrinianum</placeName>, insuper et omnem illam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs>, quam <persName key="#Queen"
                            ref="#people/1524">Berta</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">regina</rs> ex <geogName ref="#estates/1406"
                            >Camarino</geogName> adquisivit in <rs key="#Mountains">monte
                            Ferentino</rs> et Ama in <geogName ref="#estates/2352"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Muglano</geogName> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">sortem</rs> de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2355">Lauro</geogName> et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/79">Ugo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs> eiusdem Berte filius cum <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >sancti Marini</orgName> monasterio sancte Flore concessit, cum <rs
                            key="#Churches">capella</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1457">sancti Mame</orgName> et eius
                        pertinentiis, quam quidam <persName><name ref="Godalprandus"
                                >Godolprandus</name></persName> per <rs key="#Cartula #Venditio"
                            >cartam vendictionis</rs> prefato monasterio dedit et <persName
                            key="#Abbots"><name ref="Arnon">Arnon</name></persName> eius <rs
                            key="#Abbots">preposito</rs>, atque <rs key="#Mansi">mansum</rs> de
                            <placeName>Gragnano</placeName> cum pertinentiis eius, sicut actenus
                        rectus fuerat per <persName><name ref="Ianuarius"
                            >Ianuarium</name></persName> et nunc tenetur per <persName><name
                                ref="Leo/Crassus">Leonem Crassum</name></persName> et consortes eius
                        et <persName key="#Abbots"><name ref="Rodulfus">Rodulfum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbatem</rs>, cum ecclesia quam ipse ibi statuit, sicut
                        regiae actenus potestati pertinuit, nec non etiam <rs key="#Castle"
                            >castellum</rs> et <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> atque <rs
                            key="#Curtes">cortem</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Castle #Churches"
                            ref="#estates/2356">Bulgari</geogName> et <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >corticellam</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2357">Cellule</geogName> cum omnibus earum pertinentiis
                        cum <placeName>Scegi</placeName> et in <placeName>Monticello</placeName> et
                        in <placeName>Uualdinano</placeName> et in <placeName ref="#places/2766"
                            >Biuignano</placeName> et in <placeName>Campille</placeName> et in
                            <placeName>Grogi</placeName>, sicut <persName key="#Judge"><name
                                ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <persName key="#legallyRecognisedUnionWith"
                                ><name ref="Berta">Berta</name></persName> eius coniux monasterio
                        sancte Flore dederunt, et omnes <rs key="#Mansi">mansos</rs> cum
                        pertinentiis et edificiis earum, quas in <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/1403">Aretino</geogName>
                        <persName key="#sonOf"><name ref="Teutius">Teuzo</name></persName> filius
                                <persName><name ref="Offredus">Offredi</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#sonOf"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        filius <persName><name ref="Ingelelmus">Ingylelmi</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Raginaldus">Rainaldus</name></persName> de
                        Rosina, <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Azo">Azzo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbyter</rs>, <persName><name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Gerardus</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Albertus"
                                >Albertus</name></persName> filii <persName><name ref="Bonizo"
                                >Bonizonis</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohannes</name></persName> Langobardus et <persName><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Dominicus</name></persName> Ardi et <persName><name
                                ref="Angelus">Angelus</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Georgius">Georgius</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Priests"><name ref="Gariprandus">Gariprandus</name></persName>
                        presbyteri et <persName><name ref="Rodulfus">Rodulfus</name></persName>
                        filius <persName><name ref="Liutwardus">Liutardi</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName> presbyter
                        et <persName><name ref="Wido">Uuido</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Griffo">Griffonis</name></persName> in loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/2733">Corsigiano</placeName> vel alii fideles christiani
                        pro amore dei eidem monasterio dederunt in <placeName>Campauana</placeName>,
                        cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> et omni <rs key="#Decima"
                            >decimatione</rs> illa, quam episcopi Aretini prefato concesserunt
                        monasterio. Omnia autem, quae ab Ugone et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/72">Lothario</persName> et a nostra clementia vel ab aliis
                        fidelibus christianis data sunt et dabuntur, ut dictum est, deo et predicto
                        monasterio, in usum et sumptum fratrum monachorum concedimus atque largimur
                        et de nostro iure et domininio in eorum ius et domininium omnimodis
                        transfundimus ac delegamus, ut in illorum stipendio predicta predia cum
                        rebus et familiis ad ea pertinentibus maneant, ipsi eorumque successores
                        aeternaliter habeant teneant firmiterque possideant. Nec non etiam omnes res
                        et familias, quas constructor eiusdem loci eiusve posteri prefato
                        contulerunt cenobio, per hoc idem preceptum eidem concedimus et confirmamus
                        cum omni <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> illa, quam quidam
                            <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Wilielmus"
                            >Uuillelmus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs> filius Aritii sancte Flore concessit.
                        Concedimus etiam abbati eiusdem loci qui pro tempore fuerit facundiam
                        eligendi sibi <rs key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities"
                            >advocatos</rs>, quales voluerit. Insuper etiam ad augendam securitatem
                        et tranquillitatem fratrum monachorum ibidem deo famulantium, quatenus eis
                        pro nobis et imperio ab eo nobis commisso orare liceat, tam ipsos monachos
                        et omnes prefatas res quamque illorum familiam et masarios cunctasque res
                        mobiles et immobiles seseque moventes eiusdem cenobii sub nostrae <rs
                            key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">defensionis mundburdum</rs> recepimus
                        precipientes, ut nullus dux marchio archiepiscopus episcopus comes aut
                        quislibet mortalium predictum cenobium eiusque rectores suamve familiam de
                        rebus suis absque legali iudicio devestire tollere molestare minuare vel in
                        aliquo ledere audeat. Si quis igitur huius precepti et mundburdium violator
                        violator extiterit, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi
                            libras centum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis">medietatem camere
                            nostre</rs> et <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem
                            predicto cenobio et fratribus ibi deo famulantibus</rs>. Quod ut verius
                        credatur diligentiusque ab omnibus observetur, manu propria roborantes hanc
                        paginam sigillare iussimus. Signum domni Heinrici (M.) imperatoris
                        invictissimi.   <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Teudericus"
                                >Theodericus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> vice <persName
                            key="#Archchaplain #Bishops"><name ref="Everardus"
                            >Eberhardi</name></persName>
                        <orgName>Papebergiensis aecclesiae</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchaplain"
                            >archicappellani</rs> notavi. (SI. D.) Data X. kal. aug. anno
                        incarnationis domini millesimo XXIIo, indictione V, anno vero domni Heinrici
                        regnantis secundi XXIo, imperii vero VIIII; actum
                            <placeName>Priuaria</placeName> in comitatu <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/210">Lucensae</geogName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
